=== 2015 IMMAF European Open Championships of Amateur MMA ===
The 2015 IMMAF European Open Championships of Amateur MMA took place at [[Birmingham, England]], United Kingdom from the 19 to 22 November 2015.

The foundational European event took place in Birmingham at the Walsall Sports Centre at the University of Wolverhampton and was broadcast post-event on [[Ultimate Fighting Championship|UFC]] Fight Pass and international television.

